equipmentSlots.name: Demon horn necklace
equipmentSlots.breakdownNotes: Will sustain prayer with bonecrusher and enough prayer bonus. If bonecrusher is not on toolbelt, bring it in inventory.
equipmentSlots.label: demonhorn

equipmentSlots.name: Abyssal scourge
equipmentSlots.breakdownNotes: Any high tier mainhand will work.
equipmentSlots.label: abyssalscourge

equipmentSlots.name: Dark Sliver of Leng
equipmentSlots.breakdownNotes: T85 offhand leng will also work.
equipmentSlots.label: lengoh

equipmentSlots.name: Masterwork platelegs
equipmentSlots.breakdownNotes: Just for scavenging, any legs will work. Can replace with dragon rider for prayer bonus if scav is not desired.
equipmentSlots.label: mwlegs

equipmentSlots.name: Ring of Fortune
equipmentSlots.breakdownNotes: Only t2 luck is required at chaos elemental. Use any luck ring you wish, or a ring with prayer bonus.
equipmentSlots.label: ringoffortune

equipmentSlots.name: Tirannwn quiver 4
equipmentSlots.breakdownNotes: Just for prayer bonus, a rune pouch can also work.
equipmentSlots.label: quiver4

equipmentSlots.name: Scripture of Jas
equipmentSlots.breakdownNotes: Any gwd3 scripture will work. It is not turned on, just used for prayer bonus.
equipmentSlots.label: scriptureofjas
